# Role-Offer Layouts They Love

These five **role-offer** comps are proven winners with the team. Keep them available as editable Templates — separate from Real People Studio Profile.

## Family vs Real People

| Family | Use | Do not |
|--------|-----|--------|
| **Role-Offer** (this rule) | Stock/AI person crops · role pills · checklists · price/CTA · grid plate | Put named Talent Pool people here |
| **Real People / Treatment E** | Meet {Name} · role · Available to interview · no checklist/price/CTA on image | Paste these checklist layouts onto Talent portraits |

## The five layouts (1:1)

1. **`ROLE_CENTER_CHECKLIST_COLLAGE`** — Medical Admin · centered logo + “Hire a Virtual” + role pill · headline · check list + `$10` circle · 3 tilted photo strip
2. **`ROLE_SPLIT_PHOTO_LEFT`** — Medical Biller · person left · headline + bullets + bordered “STARTING AT $10/hour” box right
3. **`ROLE_SPLIT_COPY_LEFT`** — Dental Admin · audience pill (e.g. DENTISTS!) · copy + CTA left · person + price circle right
4. **`ROLE_SPLIT_COPY_PRICE_LEFT`** — Medical Nurse · audience pill · headline + checks + price bar left · person + CTA right
5. **`ROLE_PILL_CHECKLIST_SPLIT`** — Medical Admin burnout · DOCTORS! + logo · headline + role pill + checks + CTA left · person + price overlay right

## Visual DNA (match refs)

- Light grid plate (white → soft cyan), Be Vietnam, brand teal (`#077999` / `#00B2E2` / `#0D546B`)
- “Hire a Virtual” + dark teal **role pill** (white type)
- Checklist with circular check icons (or plain dots on Biller)
- Price as circle stamp **or** bordered/rounded box — editable, do not invent new rates
- Scrubs + headset stock/AI people OK on this family; colored MedVirtual logo

## Editable handoff

Source of truth: `scripts/role-offer-templates-data.mjs` → `public/role-offer-templates.html`  
All copy, bullets, icons, price, CTA, audience pill, and photo slots are data-driven / in-page editable. Refs: `public/assets/role-offer-refs/`.

Rebuild: `npm run generate:role-offer`
